- **Architecture**: Modular header-based design (no separate .c files, all implementation in headers)
- **Compilation Flow**: Lexer → Parser → AST → Symbol Table Layout → Codegen → Emit

### File Sizes (by line count)
```
main.c          4,339 lines  (driver, tests)
codegen.h       1,534 lines  (code generation)
parser.h          941 lines  (statement & expression parsing)
types.h           354 lines  (type descriptor management)
ast.h             328 lines  (AST node pool & manipulation)
emit.h            289 lines  (assembly output buffer & emission)
symtab.h          268 lines  (symbol table management)
lexer.h           263 lines  (tokenization)
layout.h          262 lines  (memory layout & frame allocation)
io.h              121 lines  (UART output utilities)
str.h              94 lines  (string utilities)
arena.h            46 lines  (memory arena allocator)
token.h           229 lines  (token types & keyword table)
```

